    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯战争加剧了工资螺旋式上升，威胁到军队征兵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/russia-s-war-fuels-a-wage-spiral-that-threatens-army-recruitment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争加剧了工人的严重短缺，这对从金属精炼厂到莫斯科豪华餐馆的企业造成了打击，并引发了加薪竞赛，威胁到克里姆林宫补充武装部队的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/russia-s-war-fuels-a-wage-spiral-that-threatens-army-recruitment</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国官员加大措辞提振市场信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/china-officials-step-up-rhetoric-to-lift-stock-market-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国当局加大了政策支持的力度，以稳定市场信心，突显出他们更加重视遏制股市暴跌。]]></description>
