    <item>
      <title>莫迪借宗教浪潮力争第三次执政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/modi-rides-religious-wave-in-bid-to-clinch-third-term-in-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪 (Narendra Modi) 开放了一座备受争议的印度教寺庙，模糊了宗教与政治之间的界限，挑战了印度的世俗传统。然而，就在距离选举仅几个月的时候，人们对这位领导人无可争议的统治地位几乎没有任何怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/modi-rides-religious-wave-in-bid-to-clinch-third-term-in-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 04:08:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
